reaking deconstruction of the perennial philosophical themes of time and desire as well as pressing contemporary issues of sovereignty and democracy.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 7aPHILOSOPHY / Movements / Deconstruction.2bisacsh40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780804779753423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780804779753/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles